  <para lang="en">
    The Align tool is useful to align various image objects.
  </para>
  <para lang="de">
    Mit diesem Werkzeug können Sie Ebenen oder andere Objekte anordnen und
    ausrichten.
  </para>
  <para lang="it">
    Lo strumento di allineamento serve ad allineare vari tipi di oggetti
    nell'immagine.
  </para>


  <sect3>
    <title>
      <phrase lang="en">Activate Tool</phrase>
      <phrase lang="cs">Aktivace nástroje</phrase>
      <phrase lang="de">Werkzeugaufruf</phrase>
      <phrase lang="es">Activación de la herramienta</phrase>
      <phrase lang="fr">Activation de l'outil</phrase>
      <phrase lang="it">Attivazione dello strumento</phrase>
      <phrase lang="no">Aktivering</phrase>
      <phrase lang="ru">Активизация инструмента</phrase>
      <phrase lang="zh_CN">启动工具</phrase>
    </title>

    <para lang="en">You can activate the Align tool in several ways :</para>
    <para lang="de">
      Sie haben verschiedene Möglichkeiten, das Werkzeug
      <quote>Ausrichten</quote> zu aktivieren:
    </para>

    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para lang="en">
          From the image-menu, through:
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu><accel>T</accel>ools</guimenu>
            <guisubmenu><accel>T</accel>ransform Tools</guisubmenu>
            <guimenuitem><accel>A</accel>lign</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>
        </para>
        <para lang="de">
          Über das Menü
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu><accel>W</accel>erkzeuge</guimenu>
            <guisubmenu><accel>T</accel>ransformationen</guisubmenu>
            <guimenuitem><accel>A</accel>usrichten</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>
          im Bildfenster,
        </para>
        <para lang="it">
          Lo strumento di allineamento può essere richiamato tramite la
          voce di menù:
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu>S<accel>t</accel>rumenti</guimenu>
            <guisubmenu>Strumenti di <accel>t</accel>rasformazione</guisubmenu>
            <guimenuitem><accel>A</accel>llinea</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>.
        </para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para lang="en">
          By clicking on the tool icon:
          <guiicon>
            <inlinemediaobject>
              <imageobject>
                <imagedata fileref='../images/toolbox/stock-tool-align-22.png' />
              </imageobject>
            </inlinemediaobject>
          </guiicon>
          in the Toolbox,
        </para>
        <para lang="cs">
          Nástroj lze také vyvolat kliknutím na ikonu spreje v Panelu
          nástrojů:
          <guiicon>
            <inlinemediaobject>
              <imageobject>
                <imagedata fileref='../images/toolbox/stock-tool-align-22.png' />
              </imageobject>
            </inlinemediaobject>
          </guiicon>
        </para>
        <para lang="de">
          mit einem Mausklick auf das Symbol
          <guiicon>
            <inlinemediaobject>
              <imageobject>
                <imagedata
                  fileref="../images/toolbox/stock-tool-align-22.png" />
              </imageobject>
            </inlinemediaobject>
          </guiicon> im Werkzeugfenster sowie
        </para>
        <para lang="es">
          La herramienta también puede activarse clicando en el icono:
          <guiicon>
            <inlinemediaobject>
              <imageobject>
                <imagedata
                  fileref='../images/toolbox/stock-tool-align-22.png' />
              </imageobject>
            </inlinemediaobject>
          </guiicon>
        </para>
        <para lang="fr">
          en cliquant sur l'icône de l'outil :
          <guiicon>
            <inlinemediaobject>
              <imageobject>
                <imagedata fileref='../images/toolbox/stock-tool-align-22.png' />
              </imageobject>
            </inlinemediaobject>
          </guiicon> dans la Boîte à Outils
        </para>
        <para lang="it">
          Lo strumento può inoltre essere richiamato tramite la relativa
          icona:
          <guiicon>
            <inlinemediaobject>
              <imageobject>
                <imagedata fileref='../images/toolbox/stock-tool-align-22.png' />
              </imageobject>
            </inlinemediaobject>
          </guiicon>
        </para>
        <para lang="no">
          ved å klikke på symbolet
          <guiicon>
            <inlinemediaobject>
              <imageobject>
                <imagedata fileref="../images/toolbox/stock-tool-align-22.png" />
              </imageobject>
            </inlinemediaobject>
          </guiicon>
          i verktøyskrinet
        </para>
        <para lang="ru">
          Инструмент также можно вызвать, нажав на пиктограмму:
          <guiicon>
            <inlinemediaobject>
              <imageobject>
                <imagedata
                  fileref='../images/toolbox/stock-tool-align-22.png' />
              </imageobject>
            </inlinemediaobject>
          </guiicon>
        </para>
        <para lang="zh_CN">
          也可以通过点击工具图标：
          <guiicon>
            <inlinemediaobject>
              <imageobject>
                <imagedata
                  fileref='../images/toolbox/stock-tool-align-22.png' />
              </imageobject>
            </inlinemediaobject>
          </guiicon>
        </para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para lang="en">
          By using the <keycap>Q</keycap> keyboard shortcut.
        </para>
        <para lang="de">
          über das Tastenkürzel <keycap>Q</keycap>.
        </para>
        <para lang="fr">
          en utilisant le raccourci-clavier <keycap>Q</keycap>
        </para>
        <para lang="it">
          O usando la scorciatoia da tastiera <keycap>Q</keycap>.
        </para>
        <para lang="no">
          eller med tastesnarvegen <keycap>Q</keycap>.
        </para>
        <para lang="ru">
          или с помощью клавиши быстрого доступа <keycap>Q</keycap>.
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </sect3>


